title: GDVS Announces New Assistant Commissioner (Georgia Department of Veterans Services)
text: ( Source : Georgia Department of Veterans Services) The Georgia Department of Veterans Service has a new Assistant Commissioner for Field Operations & Claims. Commissioner Mike Roby announced his appointment of GDVS Claims & Appeals
